my code is:

```
.div:after {
 font-family:"Font Awesome 5 Free";
 content:"\f107";
}
```

I then opened fontawesome-all.css and looked at the @font-family calls, and there are 2 calls to the same font-family name, which is Font Awesome 5 Free.

